          Many LA kitchens still run these at 12–18 years old — we support them as long as parts remain sourceable
          through Ali Group. Honest repair-vs-replace conversation on any unit 15+ years old.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Ice storage bins</h3>
